# Tech Stack (Enforced)

| Category | Technology | Notes |
|----------|------------|-------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) | All routes in `src/app` |
| UI Library | React 19 | Server Components default |
| Language | TypeScript 5 (Strict) | No `any` types |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas + Mongoose 9 | Singleton connection |
| Auth | Clerk (`@clerk/nextjs`) | Middleware + Server Actions |
| State | TanStack Query v5 | Client fetching + caching |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 | CSS-first config |
| Components | shadcn/ui (Radix) | `src/components/ui` |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod | Shared validation schemas |
| AI/LLM | OpenAI API + Vercel AI SDK | `src/server/services/ai/*` |
| SMS | Twilio | Webhooks only |
| Dates | date-fns | Tree-shakeable |

